  sectionId (48301)
  sectionNo (19)
  orderNo 19
  title `Amendment of the Constitution (Scheduled Castes) (Part C States) Order, 1951.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_19_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_19_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00023_195432_1517807321314&sectionId=48301&sectionno=19&orderno=19&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00023_195432_1517807321314
obj_root_law_sections_19_content:
  string
  line The
  line `Constitution (Scheduled Castes) (Part C States) Order 1951, shall be amended as shown in the Second`
  line Schedule.
obj_root_law_sections_19_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_20:
  sectionId (48302)
  sectionNo (20)
  orderNo 20
  title `Amendment of section 9, Act 81 of 1952.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_20_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_20_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00023_195432_1517807321314&sectionId=48302&sectionno=20&orderno=20&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00023_195432_1517807321314
obj_root_law_sections_20_content:
  string
  line `In section 9 of the Delimitation Commission`
  line `Act, 1952 (81 of 1952), in sub-section (3), for the words "and the orders made under any of the said`
  line `Acts" the words, brackets and figures "the Himachal Pradesh and Bilaspur (New State) Act, 1954 and`
  line `the orders made under any of the said Acts" shall be substituted.`
obj_root_law_sections_20_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_21:
  sectionId (48303)
  sectionNo (21)
  orderNo 21
  title `Construction of Act 43 of 1950.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_21_content
  footnotes `1 . The words, letters and figures "and the Government of Part C States Act, 1951" omitted by the A. O. (No.3), 1956.`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00023_195432_1517807321314&sectionId=48303&sectionno=21&orderno=21&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00023_195432_1517807321314
obj_root_law_sections_21_content:
  string
  line `Any reference to Himachal Pradesh in the Representation`
  line `of the People Act, 1950 (43 of 1950), ^1`
  line `* * *, as amended by this Act shall be construed as a reference`
  line `to the new State.`
obj_root_law_sections_22:
  sectionId (48304)
  sectionNo (22)
  orderNo 22
  title `Electoral rolls of constituencies.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_22_content
  footnotes `1 . Omitted by the A. O. (No. 3), 1956.`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00023_195432_1517807321314&sectionId=48304&sectionno=22&orderno=22&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00023_195432_1517807321314
obj_root_law_sections_22_content:
  string
  line `(1) The electoral rolls of the constituencies of the existing`
  line `States shall, on and from the commencement of this Act, be deemed to be the electoral rolls of the`
  line `constituencies of the same name in the new State and shall continue in force until such rolls are`
  line `revised, or fresh rolls are prepared, in accordance with law.`
  line
  line ^1
  line `* * * * * *`
obj_root_law_sections_23:
  sectionId (48305)
  sectionNo (23)
  orderNo 23
  title `Power of Delimitation Commission to revise its orders.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_23_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_23_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00023_195432_1517807321314&sectionId=48305&sectionno=23&orderno=23&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00023_195432_1517807321314
obj_root_law_sections_23_content:
  string
  line `For the purpose of determination`
  line `of the number of seats to be allotted to the new State in the House of the People in accordance with`
  line `the provisions of sub-section (1), and distribution of those seats as well as the seats allotted to the`
  line `Legislative Assembly of the new State to territorial constituencies and delimitation thereof in`
  line `accordance with the provisions of sub-section (2) of section 8 of the Delimitation Commission Act,`
  line `1952 (81 of 1952), it shall be lawful for the Delimitation Commission, notwithstanding anything`
  line `contained in that Act, to Amend, vary or rescind any of its final orders published under section 9 of`
  line `that Act in so far as any such order relates to any or both of the existing States.`
obj_root_law_sections_23_footnotes:
  string
